data.description: Welcome to this exquisite Craftsman-style residence, boasting timeless stone accents, low-maintenance vinyl siding, and a charming covered front porch, all nestled in the highly sought-after Jackson High district. As you step through the impressive 2-story foyer, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that bathes this home in a warm, inviting glow. Upon entering, the formal dining room welcomes you with its elegant heavy molding and convenient butler's pantry. The spacious kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring rich wood cabinets, an inviting eat-in area with a generous island, a built-in desk for organization, a double-door pantry, ceramic backsplash, durable plank flooring, and a complete appliance package that includes a smooth top range, microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator. This kitchen seamlessly flows into the family room, where a striking stone-surround fireplace takes center stage. Conveniently located on the first floor, a powder bath with a pedestal sink adds a touch of sophistication. Upstairs, the master suite awaits with its vaulted ceiling, ample walk-in closets, separated sink vanities, tile flooring, a relaxing garden tub, and a separate shower for your daily pampering. Bedrooms 2, 3, and 4 are equally spacious and offer generous closet space, and they share a well-appointed bathroom featuring tiled flooring and a linen closet. Outside, you'll find a fantastic outdoor space that includes a level driveway, a beautifully landscaped yard, and a welcoming patio on over half an acre of land. The home's location is ideal, with easy access to hwy 53, hwy 211, and I-85, making commuting and exploring the area a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Craftsman-style gem your forever home!
